Package: SeuratExporter
Type: Package
Title: Export Seurat Objects to Cell Ranger Compatible Folder
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Stefan Lang
Maintainer: Stefan Lang <stefan.lang@med.lu.se>
Description: Provides a simple utility to export Seurat objects into 
    a Cell Ranger-style folder structure, including matrix.mtx.gz, 
    barcodes.tsv.gz, features.tsv.gz, metadata, and embeddings (.drc files).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Imports:
    Seurat,
    Matrix,
    R.utils
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
